Description:
    Creates a new web app with angular, gulp, and requirejs.

Example:
    yo gulp-angular-requirejs

    This will create:
    	README.md: App readme
        gulpfile.js: Configuration for the task runner.
        bower.json: Front-end packages installed by bower.
        package.json: Development packages installed by npm.
        .bowerrc: Bower config
        .editorconfig: Editor config settings
        .gitignore: Git ignore file
        .gitattributes: Git attributes
        .jshintrc: jshint config
        .travis.yml: Travis-CI config

        app/: Your application files.
        test/: Unit tests for your application.
